sequenceDiagram
    participant F as Flutter客户端
    participant G as NestJS后端
    participant DB as SQLite数据库
    participant JWT as JwtService

    F->>G: POST /api/auth/login (username, password)
    G->>DB: 查询User表
    DB-->>G: 返回用户记录
    G->>G: bcrypt比对密码哈希
    G->>JWT: 签发Access Token(30min)
    G->>JWT: 签发Refresh Token(7天)
    JWT-->>G: 返回令牌对
    G-->>F: 返回{accessToken, refreshToken}
    F->>F: 存储令牌到本地安全存储
